author: Nikunj C. Oza and Stuart J. Russell
title: Online Bagging and Boosting
venue: Computer Science Division University of California
window: AdaBoost performed significantly worse and online boosting performed marginally worse. On the Car Evaluation and Chess datasets, AdaBoost and online boosting performed significantly better than Naive Bayes. On the Nursery dataset, AdaBoost performed significantly better and online boosting performed marginally better. 5
